lyrics:
[verse]
I walked alone under the moonlight glow
With a heartache that I couldn't let go
Love betrayed me, left me feeling so low
In the darkness, searching for a love I'll never know

[chorus]
Oh, this is a sad love song I sing
With every word, a tear it brings
But I'll keep hoping, I'll keep holding on
Believing one day, my heart will find its home
